# PhysicsCapture — Module Group A: Capture & Sync

## Full Implementation Plan

**Version:** 1.0  
**Target Module Group:** A — Capture & Sync  
**Submodules Covered:**

1. Camera Capture Client (PWA)
2. Local Recording via `MediaRecorder`
3. Continuous Visual Kinematic Sync (The Visual Metronome)
4. Sync Analysis (Python post-processing)

**Treating as fixed external systems:** Calibration, Ball Tracking (SAM2), Physics Engine, 3D Reconstruction, gRPC layer, Results UI.

