         ▼
[Python] SyncAnalysisPipeline.run_sync_analysis()
  ├── DotTracker (cam0): SAM2 → DotTrackingResult       (in memory)
  ├── DotTracker (cam1): SAM2 → DotTrackingResult       (in memory)
  ├── LinearFitter (cam0): → LinearFitResult            (in memory)
  ├── LinearFitter (cam1): → LinearFitResult            (in memory)
  ├── PhaseOffsetExtractor: → phase_offset_ms           (in memory)
  ├── TimestampArrayBuilder (cam0): → float64[N]        (in memory)
  └── TimestampArrayBuilder (cam1): → float64[M]        (in memory)
         │
