| `POST /api/upload-video`          | Phone PWA                         | HTTP                    |
| `RunSyncAnalysis` gRPC            | Node.js (after ffmpeg completes)  | gRPC                    |

### 7.2 Exit Points From This Module Group

| Exit Point                                     | Consumer                                     | Data                     |
| ---------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| `sync.json` written to disk                    | Physics Engine (`fitting.py`)                | Master timestamp array   |
| `sync.json` written to disk                    | Ball Tracking (validation; timestamp lookup) | `timestamp_ms` per frame |
