**[E5] TimestampArrayBuilder:**

- Input: `frame_count=10`, `true_fps=30.0`, `phase_offset_ms=13.74`.
- Assert output = `[13.74, 47.11, 80.47, 113.84, ...]` ± 0.01ms.
- Assert monotonically increasing.

