| Recommendation                 | For experiments > 30s, issue a warning; for > 120s, show a hard limit message                                                     |
| Mitigation                     | 1-second `timeslice` on `MediaRecorder` avoids accumulating one giant Blob; however all chunks are still held in RAM until upload |

